reviewText: This movie was bad.  The F word was used way to much which was very annoying.  Story line was boring too.
A waste of time.  Very inane movie.
Excellent movie. Great story, slow paced but rewarding if you stick with it. Some laugh out loud moments. Tyler is a very good actor!
strange but it was an okay movie once you got past all the f'words.
Bought for family to watch during Christmas....unfortunately no one thought was that great, others may like it though....
Strong performances by Tyler Labine & Chace Crawford, solid writing & directing. 100% worth checking out!

Every other word was the F-bomb.  Sometimes it was 5 or 7 times in a row.  Even if the language had been cleaned up and the vocabulary increased, the screenplay was lacking miserably.  The storyline is not all that bad - it just got into the wrong hands.  It could have been a good, funny, entertaining and adventurous movie but they ruined it.  It's not even going on the shelf.
A good movie. I enjoyed it.
